### Fraud Detection Service API Tests

### 1. Check Fraud - Low Risk (Small Amount, Existing User)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "transactionId": 1,
  "carId": 1,
  "amount": 300000,
  "ipAddress": "103.45.67.89",
  "deviceId": "device_123",
  "location": "Mumbai"
}

### 2. Check Fraud - Medium Risk (High Amount)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "transactionId": 2,
  "carId": 2,
  "amount": 1200000,
  "ipAddress": "103.45.67.90",
  "deviceId": "device_456",
  "location": "Delhi"
}

### 3. Check Fraud - High Risk (New User, High Amount)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 999,
  "transactionId": 3,
  "carId": 3,
  "amount": 1500000,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "deviceId": "device_789",
  "location": "Unknown"
}

### 4. Check Fraud - Critical Risk (Very High Amount, Suspicious IP)
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 998,
  "transactionId": 4,
  "carId": 4,
  "amount": 2500000,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.0.1",
  "deviceId": "device_suspicious",
  "location": "Unknown"
}

### 5. Get Fraud Check by Transaction ID
GET http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/transaction/1

### 6. Check Fraud - Multiple Transactions Same User
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "transactionId": 5,
  "carId": 5,
  "amount": 800000,
  "ipAddress": "103.45.67.89",
  "deviceId": "device_123",
  "location": "Mumbai"
}

### 7. Check Fraud - Rapid Transaction
POST http://localhost:8088/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "transactionId": 6,
  "carId": 6,
  "amount": 500000,
  "ipAddress": "103.45.67.89",
  "deviceId": "device_123",
  "location": "Mumbai"
}
